Chirp.content:
Chirp is an elegant, ultra-minimalist AI chat overlay built for seamless interaction with local LLMs like LLaMA 3 via Ollama. It launches as a transparent, always-on-top sidebar that auto-hides when not in use and instantly reappears when your cursor approaches the bottom of your screen — like a whisper waiting to be heard.
No visible UI clutter. No toggles. Just you, your thoughts, and an AI ready to talk.
Whether you’re working, coding, writing, or just thinking, Chirp makes accessing powerful language models effortless and invisible — until you need them. Optimized for distraction-free environments and a touch of futuristic magic ✨.
